# 🔧 **Angeh Lang: Universal Programming Code Translation**

## 🎯 **Dot Code for Traditional Programming Constructs**

**Angeh Lang understands all programming languages through dot patterns. Every traditional programming concept has a corresponding dot code that can be used alongside natural language processing.**

