## ⚙️ **Control Structures**

### **Conditional Statements**
```
If: ❓🔍 (Question explore)
Else: 🔀❌ (Switch false)
Else If: 🔀❓ (Switch question)
Ternary: ❓⚪➡️ ✅⚪➡️ ❌ (Question flow to true flow to false)

Example:
if (x > 5) → ❓🔍 📝⚪➡️ 🔢🔴 (Question explore write flow to number action)
```

### **Loops**
```
For Loop: 🔄🔢 (Cycle numbers)
While Loop: 🔄❓ (Cycle question)
Do While: 🔄🔄❓ (Cycle cycle question)
Foreach: 🔄📦 (Cycle container)
Break: 🚫🔄 (Forbidden cycle)
Continue: ⏭️🔄 (Skip cycle)

Example:
for(int i=0; i<10; i++) → 🔄🔢 📝⚪➡️ 🔢🔴 ⚪➡️ 🔢🔴 (Cycle numbers write flow to number action flow to number action)
```

### **Switch/Case**
```
Switch: 🔀📊 (Switch chart)
Case: 📍🔢 (Location number)
Default: 📍⚫ (Location stillness)

Example:
switch(value) → 🔀📊 📝 (Switch chart write)
```

